---
layout: base
title: "Message Received"
description: Your message has been received. Here's what happens next.
permalink: /thank-you/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<div class="container ty-page">
  <div class="ty-wrap">

    {# ── Hero ── #}
    <header class="ty-hero">
      <div class="ty-hero__check" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 52 52" width="64" height="64" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="26" cy="26" r="24" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.2"/>
          <path d="M14 27l8 8 16-18" class="ty-hero__check-path"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <p class="ty-hero__kicker">Received</p>
      <h1 class="ty-hero__title">Your message is in good hands.</h1>
      <p class="ty-hero__lede">
        Thank you for writing. Every message is read by an editor &mdash; not a bot, not a template filter.
      </p>
    </header>

    {# ── What happens next ── #}
    <section class="ty-steps" aria-label="What happens next">
      <h2 class="ty-section__heading">What happens next</h2>
      <ol class="ty-steps__list">
        <li class="ty-step">
          <span class="ty-step__num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
          <div>
            <p class="ty-step__title">An editor reads it</p>
            <p class="ty-step__desc">Usually within one business day. We read in the order received.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="ty-step">
          <span class="ty-step__num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
          <div>
            <p class="ty-step__title">We decide if it needs a reply</p>
            <p class="ty-step__desc">Questions and correction requests always get a response. Tips and feedback are logged even when we don&rsquo;t write back.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="ty-step">
          <span class="ty-step__num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
          <div>
            <p class="ty-step__title">If a reply is coming, it&rsquo;s from a person</p>
            <p class="ty-step__desc">Expect an email within a few business days &mdash; signed by the editor who picked it up.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    {# ── Subscribe card ── #}
    <section class="ty-card" aria-label="Subscribe to the newsletter">
      <p class="ty-card__kicker">While you&rsquo;re here</p>
      <h2 class="ty-card__title">Get our next piece in your inbox</h2>
      <p class="ty-card__body">One email, occasionally. No tracking pixels, no third-party data sharing, unsubscribe with one click.</p>
      <div class="ty-card__form">
        {% set subscribeVariant = "inline" %}
        {% include "partials/subscribe.njk" %}
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── Read next grid ── #}
    <section class="ty-next" aria-label="Read next">
      <h2 class="ty-section__heading">Read next</h2>
      <div class="ty-next__grid">
        <a class="ty-next__card" href="/start-here/">
          <p class="ty-next__kicker">Orientation</p>
          <p class="ty-next__title">Start here &rarr;</p>
          <p class="ty-next__desc">What this publication is, who pays for it, and how it works.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="ty-next__card" href="/editorial/">
          <p class="ty-next__kicker">Policy</p>
          <p class="ty-next__title">Editorial handbook &rarr;</p>
          <p class="ty-next__desc">Our standards for accuracy, sourcing, corrections, and tone.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="ty-next__card" href="/library/">
          <p class="ty-next__kicker">Deep reading</p>
          <p class="ty-next__title">The library &rarr;</p>
          <p class="ty-next__desc">Public-domain works &mdash; freethought, philosophy, dissent.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="ty-next__card" href="/archives/">
          <p class="ty-next__kicker">Everything</p>
          <p class="ty-next__title">Browse archives &rarr;</p>
          <p class="ty-next__desc">Search and filter by section, author, and year.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── Quick links ── #}
    <nav class="ty-quicklinks" aria-label="Quick links">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <span class="ty-quicklinks__sep" aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
      <a href="/corrections/">Corrections log</a>
      <span class="ty-quicklinks__sep" aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
      <a href="/contact/">Contact desk</a>
      <span class="ty-quicklinks__sep" aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
      <a href="/random/">Surprise me</a>
    </nav>

  </div>
</div>

